Undo: press esc and the u 
to view a file : cat Filename
to edit a file: vi filename
to enter the text press i and then enter
to save the file press esc and then:wq
to exit the file without saving the changes press :q

to check Port: netstat -lntp
to check ip: hostname -ip
View last modified files: ls -lt
lsof -i:<Port> To know what is running on the port
